{"tid":762663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港五大必去景點！第一名是甚麼大家都知道了！","createTime":"2018-07-31T13:00:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T15:22:59.000Z","uid":31219,"like":7,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"6c455b5ce841e0c8451a4ca9199703f8ca8e5197","tid":762663,"uid":31219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T13:00:42.000Z","msg":"No.5 香港海洋公園<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/204953_2ab8d8c4e59b052a19e0bc56ff70e4c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F204953_2ab8d8c4e59b052a19e0bc56ff70e4c8.jpg&h=2028b6ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港知名度極高的主題樂園，分為高峰樂園、海濱樂園，佔地極廣可玩上一整天。除了欣賞國寶級動物、近距離接觸動物外，還有刺激度極高的遊樂設施，每年萬聖節更是精采，波比被嚇的尖叫聲連連，隨時會撞鬼的恐懼，非常適合年輕人來挑戰～<br />\n<br />\nNo.4 香港迪士尼樂園<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/205140_1e024f33cc47c5f7c432f29854b21257.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F205140_1e024f33cc47c5f7c432f29854b21257.jpg&h=e2ac618b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本東京迪士尼樂園後，亞洲第二座迪士尼主題樂園。由七大主題園區組成，美國小鎮大街、探險世界、明日世界、玩具總動員大本營等，萬聖節、過年還有特別活動，一家老小都適合，波比人生第一座迪士尼樂園，念念不忘啊～<br />\n<br />\nNo.3 維多利亞港（幻彩詠香江、張保仔號、星光大道）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/205238_050cc32b4a7bce381bf29e08ad20e1a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F205238_050cc32b4a7bce381bf29e08ad20e1a7.jpg&h=8e9882a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n全球最大音樂燈光秀，與維多利亞港47棟建築物合作，結合雷射燈、LED燈與背景音樂，十餘年來吸引超過400萬人觀賞。搭乘古色古香的張保仔號，啜飲雞尾酒是最享受的觀賞方式。一旁的星光大道也是重點，無數明星手印和簽名，不過目前正在整修，預計2018年年底開放～<br />\n<br />\nNo.2 太平山頂（纜車、百萬夜景、杜莎夫人蠟像館）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/205411_b7da04d47b55722bb14dbc8c27c9bee3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F205411_b7da04d47b55722bb14dbc8c27c9bee3.jpg&h=8bd8ced7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港最經典的玩法，搭山頂纜車到凌霄閣摩天台欣賞太平山百萬夜景～時間夠的話再去杜莎夫人蠟像館狂拍照、阿甘蝦餐廳大啖美食就更完美了。維港絢麗景緻眾人愛，不想排到天荒地老的人，務必買纜車快速通關票啊!!!"},{"pid":"d7a67c9bd0bb9ed9a50c6b3639ccc69fc7ed232d","tid":762663,"uid":31219,"like":46,"dislike":21,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T13:00:48.000Z","msg":"No.1 金鐘M記<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/210031_c62ed00693d440bd6aa39d097514a986.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F210031_c62ed00693d440bd6aa39d097514a986.jpg&h=c8d114b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n難得到香港旅遊，當然不要錯過這個突破次元的機會，早就決定聖巡「金鐘M記」。香港金鐘的美國菜漢堡包快餐店，客人每天都來得絡繹不絕，生意非常興旺。廢話少講，就讓我們來展開聖巡之旅吧～"},{"pid":"ba72dcc4d1713ae1ea653ff3b4acca6532d3e494","tid":762663,"uid":181162,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T13:02:42.000Z","msg":"本身有5分，最後一張扣4.9分<br />\n0.1/10"},{"pid":"8d4ea8a6174ab302f2e426ac0f74b83c2c5be52f","tid":762663,"uid":94167,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T13:11:45.000Z","msg":"樓主on9"},{"pid":"0fe53fb209026a25ff65ebd49a0dce5689f59207","tid":762663,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T13:12:43.000Z","msg":"樓主好波"},{"pid":"0ef8cbe54b1563713a91655865933a3100709872","tid":762663,"uid":97494,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T13:12:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"680d5a4629a553e17b7a2553bada5e14af48063a","tid":762663,"uid":95397,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T13:12:58.000Z","msg":"唔好怪樓主<br />\n佢個腦唔好"},{"pid":"c8d8a0df7f79ed4641279be2aa5b8b0024ea2b67","tid":762663,"uid":2794,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T13:13:45.000Z","msg":"你個腦唔好 負評ed"},{"pid":"2a528028743fcb7a8d106a79b7e67beb105d161c","tid":762663,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1